{"tid":1519710,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"睇完咁多新聞覺得驚嘅入嚟，You are not alone.","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T02:23:36.000Z","uid":243854,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f16ef59ddffe352861dd79552f41f5301dc73865","tid":1519710,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"我想話畀大家知，大家多多少少都俾今日嘅白色恐怖氛圍影響到<br />\n但相比起我哋，我反而覺得港共先係最驚果個<br />\n因為佢哋根本無能力制止人民嘅行動(中共禁止撤回)。<br />\n所以狗急跳牆捉晒啲出名嘅人嚟祭旗，營造更恐怖氛圍(捉無名義士，大家唔識佢哋感覺唔到實在消失視線中，而出名嘅人就營造到眼前嘅人少咗。)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以大家咪撚驚，今次同2014唔同，我哋無大台，無再分化，無再割席。<br />\n而且喺民意仲係支持大家，即係至少呢二百萬都係同大家同一陣線，所以我哋唔係孤軍作戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信我哋可以不停進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直到得到五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家驚就入嚟傾下對策，順便當緊張感係提醒緊我哋唔可以太過放鬆，否則就自亂陣腳！"},{"pid":"6173b4f86fa51e699e56ace6ff31e53d4b66e880","tid":1519710,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"驚佢老尾<br />\n<br />\n【新冷戰】緊急法 -&gt; 機場塞停 -&gt; 美軍派艦撒僑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519582</a>"},{"pid":"56133d8d1b6c941ec15cd2ca7d383a94d5cd9643","tid":1519710,"uid":108347,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"D人係淆冇左分工<br />\n<br />\n其實你認真諗下,你所謂養家供樓,你唔出黎幾年後大家一齊住集中營係唔再需要養家同供樓<br />\n<br />\n而家即係生CANCER,你同我講你放棄等死就一回事,冇人怪你,但係你同我講因為怕辛苦怕甩頭髮,不如我唔做化療搏下佢唔擴散....其實係好傻"},{"pid":"52123add08edb6b8abf0ec5554474a5e4be7d8a3","tid":1519710,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6173b4f86fa51e699e56ace6ff31e53d4b66e880","tid":1519710,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"驚佢老尾<br />\n<br />\n【新冷戰】緊急法 -&gt; 機場塞停 -&gt; 美軍派艦撒僑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519582</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講真，驚就真係唔係驚<br />\n但真係俾呢個恐怖氣氛搞到有少少似睇緊鬼片等驚嚇位咁"},{"pid":"e66f068cb1279079b381c1ad47fb466f8b9d8282","tid":1519710,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:43:34.000Z","msg":"8.31不是endgame！大家係咪已經忘記天琦講過咩啦？<br />\n不要被仇恨支配自己，時刻保持警覺與思考 <br />\n- <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519685</a>"},{"pid":"fccbbec76a2c728d3d2953a56363b05361db5ead","tid":1519710,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"聽日打游擊戰！試吓去未夢遊過既地方發夢！"},{"pid":"196e7b9f2c8ef896d9fd32c005b85d77eac3a2ef","tid":1519710,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:45:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519280/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519280/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">We Are In The End Game Now<br />\n只要行落去就會贏<br />\n831係其中一役, 但一定要贏, 一定要夠人</span></strong>"},{"pid":"dbc2a0d4c0a35f153f63003768e2443e380208b2","tid":1519710,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:46:00.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr